{"tid":1133738,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天文台：市民認為天文台發出的天氣預測有77%是準確的","createTime":"2019-05-01T09:55:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T10:08:33.000Z","uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"10d80f20c19856c1f205274bd46febedbd06e7d9","tid":1133738,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T09:55:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hko.gov.hk/abouthko/pledgec.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fabouthko%2Fpledgec.htm&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEPiPq%2FHqG0pMUyXzarzxqBM%3D&h=4ff4d575\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hko.gov.hk/abouthko/pledgec.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n意見調查<br />\n<br />\n我們每年委托獨立調查公司定期進行公眾意見調查，以了解市民對天文台的天氣預測之準確程度及整體服務水平的意見。2017年的公眾意見調查顯示（圖一），市民認為天文台發出的天氣預測有77%是準確的。至於天文台的整體服務水平，市民給予的平均分數為7.6（10分為滿分）（圖二）。"},{"pid":"b0856dfbf889eb56412719a8b406069b0bffc1c2","tid":1133738,"uid":46654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T09:56:28.000Z","msg":"又話今日落雨？"},{"pid":"b9afcc9b274714e3453c42faf877e566f4f909e9","tid":1133738,"uid":42188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b0856dfbf889eb56412719a8b406069b0bffc1c2","tid":1133738,"uid":46654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T09:56:28.000Z","msg":"又話今日落雨？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T09:57:18.000Z","msg":"可能驚你出街阻著支那人過假期？"},{"pid":"3d5c03b0cbc9cee043d8f66c91b32ff201d30f04","tid":1133738,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:04:19.000Z","msg":"市民認為有咩用，自己有預測數據，亦都有實際數據記錄當時係咪落雨。兩個數據擺埋一齊對比咪知。理得市民評分係點，你都可以理直氣壯都公布準確率係幾多。"},{"pid":"b570b8e922ad7e35fde8ac2b701d4e525e62394c","tid":1133738,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:07:09.000Z","msg":"重要野 timing 錯曬"},{"pid":"5fe0a593517afdb950beb9d7d3296cb15af11382","tid":1133738,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:07:46.000Z","msg":"仆街，你成班科學家唔識對預測同實際數據差幾多<br />\n<br />\n出問卷咁撚